{
  "id": 6228675846209536,
  "name": "Crash Reporting key-value API",
  "summary": "A new key-value API, tentatively `window.crashReport`, backed by a per-Document map holding data that gets appended to crash reports.\n\nSee https://github.com/WICG/crash-reporting/issues/15 for initial discussion. The data placed in this API's backing map gets sent in the `CrashReportBody` [1] if any renderer process crashes are incurred by the site. This lets developers debug what specific state in their application might be causing a given crash.\n\n[1]: https://wicg.github.io/crash-reporting/#crashreportbody",
